```json
{
  "application": "Snakemake",
  "details": {
    "workflow": "GATK CNV workflow",
    "resources": {
      "singularity": "required, can be installed or loaded via module",
      "dataBundle": "required, downloaded and uncompressed from https://hci-bio-app.hci.utah.edu/gnomex/?analysisNumber=A5578",
      "container": "required, built after each update, e.g. singularity pull docker://hcibioinformatics/public:GATK_SM_2",
      "input_files": [
        "tumor.bam/.bai(or .cram/.crai)",
        "normal.bam/.bai(or .cram/.crai)",
        "tumor passing region bed file",
        "germline variant xxx.vcf.gz file with its associated index",
        "gender and capture matched PoN xxx.hdf5 and xxx.interval_list files"
      ],
      "workflow_docs": [
        "xxx.sing",
        "xxx.README.sh",
        "xxx.sm",
        "xxx.yaml snakemake config file"
      ],
      "resource_archive": "required for AWS EC2 via JobRunner, containing: Homo_sapiens_assembly38.fasta, Homo_sapiens_assembly38.dict, Homo_sapiens_assembly38.fasta.fai, public_GATK_SM_1.sif, mergedSeqCap_EZ_Exome_v3_hg38_capture_primary_targets_pad150bp.preprocessed.interval_list, hg38IdtProbesPad150bp.processed.interval_list, hg38StdChromLengths.bed.gz, hg38RefSeq8Aug2018_Merged.ucsc.gz"
    },
    "runtime": "24 hours",
    "environment": "SLURM cluster (hci-rw partition)"
  }
}
```
